==English==
===Interjection===
(Something) '''my eye'''!  Variously -'''my foot''', -'''my ass''', -'''my rear''', etc.
#indicates [[disapproval]], [[disregard]], [[disdain]], [[disgust]] or [[disbelief]] 
#:''Earache, '''my eye'''!'' -- Cheech & Chong

